{"tid":1229212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左繼續懲罰黑警之外，呢招好有用","createTime":"2019-06-16T00:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T02:15:13.000Z","uid":244332,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8533d44e4c745416c57d9713c48112c6c0487d66","tid":1229212,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:21:55.000Z","msg":"而家警察分為兩種人，<br />\n1. 明知幫緊中共 而扮唔知既人 (e.g.盧偉聰)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n        - 呢種人等如建制派議員，可以放棄<br />\n        - 真正最邪惡既黑警<br />\n        - 說服佢 等如說服建制派議員一樣咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 真心以為自己申張緊正義既藍絲腦殘警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n        - 呢種人等如師奶同廢老<br />\n        - 冇咩學歷，俾警察學堂d歪理洗哂腦<br />\n        - 等如被cctvb洗腦既廢老<br />\n        - 可以繼續俾壓力佢地，好似今次大家成功說服倒好多藍絲師奶同親戚一樣</span><br />\n<del>3. 好警察</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------<br />\n今次俾多d壓力，當佢地親戚朋友全部鬧佢地 搞到冇哂生活圈子既時候，<br />\n就算令唔倒佢地倒戈，佢地潛意識一定會就住就住唔會咁狼，對日後民主運動點都有利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"f7c38e2006224fd5c2cc03ad9a988ed04741a964","tid":1229212,"uid":39808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:36:35.000Z","msg":"全民監控黑警，見到黑警即時攝錄，以免錯過黑警犯罪時刻，全面記錄黑警罪證，注意自身安全避免單獨行動"},{"pid":"a26978ef2538d3f8c11aff2a4bac2e450ad095b1","tid":1229212,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:38:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"220e2fe3447fa291f851484c58d59f9e19cb7de3","tid":1229212,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7c